#Text=Wikinews Shorts : March 26 , 2012

#Text=Wikinews is a project of the Wikimedia Foundation .
#Text=A compilation of brief news reports for Monday , March 26 , 2012 .
#Text=Australian Broadcasting Company releases content to Wikimedia under free license
#Text=The first broadcast on ABC , November 5 , 1956

#Text=In lieu of the Australian Broadcasting Company ( ABC ) turning 80 this year , they have decided to release a collection of historic audio and visual content under a Creative Commons free license for use on Wikipedia and for use by the public .

#Text=Project officer Liam Wyatt hopes that " this release from the Australian public broadcaster will be the beginning of an ongoing relationship with the Wikimedia projects and the Wikimedia community , and encourage other broadcasters – especially those that are publicly funded – to join us . "

column1: #Text=3.1 earthquake aftershock rattles central Virginia
#Text=Another aftershock has rattled central Virginia last night .

#Text=The 3.1-magnitude earthquake was focused around Mineral , Virginia which served as the epicenter for an August 2011 earthquake that was strong enough to damage American landmarks in Washington , D.C. like the Washington Monument .
#Text=It was felt as far away as Harrisburg , Pennsylvania and Charlotte , North Carolina .
#Text=As of press time , no damage was reported .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Associated Press .
#Text=" Aftershocks from 2011 quake continue in Va , 3.1-magnitude reported 8 miles from epicenter " — Washington Post , March 26 , 2012
#Text=Benjamin R. Freed .
#Text=" Virginia Rattled by Yet Another Earthquake " — DCist , March 26 , 2012
#Text=Central Chile rocked by second earthquake in 24-hours
#Text=Central Chile experienced two earthquakes within 24 hours .
#Text=Saturday morning , at 4:28 a. m. , a magnitude 5.1 earthquake shook Santiago .
#Text=No injuries or damages were reported .
#Text=A second earthquake , of 7.1-magnitude , took place on Sunday , at 6:37 p.m. in Maule , which is approximately 219 kilometers south-south-west of Santiago .
#Text=As of this report , no injuries or major damages have been reported .
#Text=Coastal evacuations are being promoted by authorities , however , the Chilean Navy is doubtful of a tsunami .
#Text=Sources
#Text=" News of the Day From Across the Globe " — Chronicle News Services , March 25 , 2012

#Text=Tiger Woods secures first PGA Tour win in 30 months
#Text=Tiger Woods is back .
#Text=Image : Angela George .
#Text=American pro golfer Tiger Woods has secured his first PGA Tour win in 30 months , winning at the Arnold Palmer Invitational in Orlando , Florida .
#Text=This makes his seventh Arnold Palmer Invitational .
#Text=Woods beat runner up Graeme McDowell , posting a score of two-under 70 .
#Text=" Tiger 's back , " stated Jay Busbee of Yahoo ! Sports .
#Text=Sources
#Text=" Tiger Woods earns first PGA win since 2009 " — CNN , March 25 , 2012
#Text=Jay Busbee .
#Text=" Tiger Woods returns to winning ways at long last with victory at Bay Hill " — Yahoo ! Sports , March 25 , 2012
#Text=New leader of Hong Kong chosen while protestors seek ' true democracy '
#Text=Leung Chun-ying was declared the new Chief Executive of Hong Kong today .
#Text=He won 689 out of 1,193 election committee votes .
#Text=Pro-democracy protests took place throughout the weekend , including the protestors waiting for the election committee upon their arrival at the convention center to cast their votes .
#Text=The demonstrators also attempted to storm the convention center , and when election results were announced the police used pepper spray to ward off the protestors .

#Text=Demonstration organizer Avery Ng describes Hong Kong as not being a " true democracy , " with other protestors believing that Hong Kong would never gain the right to vote , which would be given to them by China .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Kevin Drew .
#Text=" Tensions Remain After Hong Kong Election " — New York Times , March 25 , 2012
#Text=Natasha Khan .
#Text=" Hong Kong Police Use Spray as Protesters Try to Storm Poll Site " — Bloomberg , March 25 , 2012
